data.description: Popular Waterford Landing is now built out and the last new construction home just sold but here is your chance to get in at an affordable price.  Measuring in at over 3000 sq ft this 4 bedroom 3 and a half bath is a lot of house for the money; compare to others in the neighborhood.  LVP was installed throughout the first floor in 2020.  The 9 foot ceilings and morning room addition provide for a very open feel.  You will love this spacious kitchen with staggered 42 inch cabinets, roll out shelves, extended island with bar seating, recessed lighting, RO system and gas stove - dishwasher was replaced last year.  The light filled morning room leads to a deck, gazebo will stay, and a fully fenced rear yard.  All the bedrooms are upstairs along with the conveniently located laundry room.  The owner’s suite features an awesome walk-in closet, 13 x 6, and the attached bath has a soaking tub, shower and double vanities.  The finished basement has a full bath with custom ceramic surround and there is still an unfinished area for storage.  Waterford’s location is ideal being so close to Wright Patterson Air Force Base and all the shopping and amenities of the Shoppes at Valle Greene and Fairfield Commons Mall.  Be sure to put this one on your list to see.  Occupancy Dec 18th.
